<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px">
    Hi <%= @registration.user.name %>!
    
    Another pilot has registered on the same channel as you for <%= @registration.event.name %>
    
    You will now be sharing <%= @registration.channel.band.name %> <%= @registration.channel.name %> (<%= @registration.channel.frequency %>) with the following pilots: 
    
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
      </tr>
      
      <% @other_pilots.each do |pilot| %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= pilot.name %></td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </table>
    
    On the day of the event please only fly when you posses the Race Duck for your channel.
    
    KillaKwads Events
  </body>
</html>